    {
      "start": 0,
      "end": 25,
      "text": "I took a walk around the world to ease my troubled mind"
    },
    {
      "start": 25,
      "end": 29,
      "text": "I left my body lying somewhere in the sands of time"
    },
    {
      "start": 29,
      "end": 34,
      "text": "But I watched the world float to the dark side of the moon"
    },
    {
      "start": 34,
      "end": 40,
      "text": "I feel there\u0027s nothing I can do, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 49,
      "end": 54,
      "text": "I watched the world float to the dark side of the moon"
    },
    {
      "start": 54,
      "end": 58,
      "text": "After all I knew it had to be something to do with you"
    },
    {
      "start": 58,
      "end": 63,
      "text": "I really don\u0027t mind what happens now and then"
    },
    {
      "start": 63,
      "end": 68,
      "text": "As long as you\u0027ll be my friend at the end"
    },
    {
      "start": 68,
      "end": 73,
      "text": "If I go crazy then will you still call me Superman?"
    },
    {
      "start": 73,
      "end": 78,
